for example?

14:11.150 --> 14:13.539
The ELM sent us
seven letters in 2008.

14:13.580 --> 14:15.411
I know that we kept hard copies
of them in our records room.

14:15.450 --> 14:16.644
You want to take a look?

14:16.680 --> 14:18.386
We would.

14:20.320 --> 14:23.483
Effluvium, fussbudget, Cairo.

14:23.530 --> 14:26.419
Nine across,
14 down, 32 down.

14:26.460 --> 14:29.623
