for puzzles.

14:34.540 --> 14:35.996
When_I first tried
getting clean,

14:36.040 --> 14:37.507
I started drinking.

14:37.540 --> 14:40.077
Before long, I realized
that I had swapped

14:40.110 --> 14:41.509
one addiction
for another.

14:41.540 --> 14:43.007
Please put those away.

14:43.050 --> 14:45.143
"You cannot stop this.
