14:47.520 --> 14:50.546
That's something
the ELM would say.

14:50.590 --> 14:52.080
Here...

14:52.120 --> 14:54.088
Not the time,
not the place.

14:54.120 --> 14:56.554
I'm sorry, but from a forensic
linguistics standpoint,

14:56.590 --> 14:58.353
these threats _are
qUIte fascmating.

