40:50.880 --> 40:52.973
Ever since I got
straightened out,

40:53.010 --> 40:55.069
I've been picking up
work with car companies.

40:55.120 --> 40:56.917
I test their
security systems.

40:56.950 --> 40:59.248
I guess they figure anything
that can keep me out

40:59.290 --> 41:01.087
is good enough for
their customers.

41:03.920 --> 41:06.127
Miss Watson tells me_that
you're into lock-picking.

41:06.160 --> 41:08.549
I figure maybe you
want to give it a shot.

41:08.600 --> 41:10.056
Well, the truth is, Alfredo,

41:10.100 --> 41:12.762
I'm already quite adept
at defeating security systems.

41:12.800 --> 41:14.961
This stuff's not even
on the market yet.

41:15.000 --> 41:16.865
So, really...

41:16.900 --> 41:18.868
how would you know
if you could beat it?

41:26.280 --> 41:29.215
You know
you want to try.

41:29.250 --> 41:31.172
Obviously your idea.

41:31.220 --> 41:33.245
Zeroing in on
common ground.

41:33.290 --> 41:35.758
Hoping it's enough
to make me reconsider him.

41:35.790 --> 41:37.519
It won't be.

41:37.560 --> 41:40.484
What's the harm in getting
to know the guy?

41:42.560 --> 41:43.925
One way or the other,

41:43.960 --> 41:46.099
I'm gonna be out
of your life in a few weeks.

41:47.230 --> 41:48.993
Maybe you're
dreading that day;

41:49.040 --> 41:51.907
maybe you're counting
the seconds.

41:51.940 --> 41:53.999
Either way,
I'm going to make sure

41:54.040 --> 41:57.168
you're ready
when the time comes.

41:57.210 --> 41:58.643
I promise.

42:03.320 --> 42:05.584
IfI help him
with his assignment,

42:05.620 --> 42:07.941
it does not mean I am assenting
to his sponsorship.

42:07.990 --> 42:09.150
Of course it doesn't.

42:09.190 --> 42:11.078
I am quite self-sufficient.

42:11.120 --> 42:13.122
Of course you are.

42:28.210 --> 42:29.905
Factory-installed
immobilizer

42:29.940 --> 42:32.044
or after-market
tracking system?

42:32.080 --> 42:33.877
Not telling.

42:36.080 --> 42:37.638
That's quite all right.

42:37.680 --> 42:40.945
I'll just figure it out
for myself.

42:40.990 --> 42:42.878
I'm entirely
self-sufficient, you know.

